        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-08-16-03-18-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:6807a96a1a3eec6b1f9f0f593e866381aa76037e6ecc486c958ec3ed944ac34ef8dbe46a54663cd6653cbc84094c357558f11375d8f7a2f5e457b62d70934eb9"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-08-16-03-18-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
